        <num>CCP 2082</num>
        <heading>2082.  Definition of appeal</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2082.  Definition of appeal
Appeal is the exercise of the right of a party to have a judgment of a trial court revised, modified, set aside, or reversed by an appellate court.</p>
        </content>
